  "description": "<h3>Nintendo.com Description (from <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/brainstorm-series-treasure-chase/adblurbs\">Ad Blurbs</a>)</h3><br><br><p style=\"margin-top: 0\">\n      This challenging thinking game goes to the next level. Take a trip to \n      exotic places around the world and find extraordinary treasures of human \n      history. More than 300\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 0\">\n      demanding puzzles on 16 different maps await you. Gaming pieces such as \n      snakes, switches and ice stones\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 0\">\n      make Treasure Chase even trickier. With a freely rotatable playing area \n      and the option of undoing your moves as often as you want, you will \n      always have an overview of the current state of play.\n    </p>\n    <p>\n      <b>Features</b>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"padding-left: 25.0px; margin-top: 0\">\n      • 360 Demanding puzzles on 16 different maps• The built in \n      solution help will assist you in your treasure hunt• DSi picture \n      function• Compete with a friend in an exciting multiplayer mode \n      against the clock\n    </p>",
